WEBVTT

00:06:27.163 --> 00:06:30.038
Va men shu holatlarda bizni ishimiz 
bo’layotgan

00:06:30.079 --> 00:06:32.121
nohaqliklarni buzish ekanligiga ishonaman.

00:06:32.121 --> 00:06:34.246
Agarda biz eng qudratlisi bo’lmasakda,

00:06:34.246 --> 00:06:36.496
bizni birga birlashganimiz

00:06:36.496 --> 00:06:37.954
bizni kuchli qiladi.

00:06:37.996 --> 00:06:40.454
Bu huddi ayolni majlisga taklif qilish,

00:06:40.496 --> 00:06:43.371
so’zini aytishga qiynalayotgan ayol

00:06:43.413 --> 00:06:46.788
yoki o’z fikrini ifodala olmaydigan 
odamning gapi eshitilishiga

00:06:46.829 --> 00:06:48.121
imkon yaratishdir.

00:06:48.163 --> 00:06:51.413
Bizning vazifamiz ular uchun imkon 
yaratish. Har bir insonning

00:06:51.454 --> 00:06:53.538
farovonligi -
bu jamoa mas’uliyatidir.

00:06:53.579 --> 00:06:55.788
Shu narsani ommaga
anglatolsak, biz yordamga

00:06:55.829 --> 00:06:57.496
muhtoj bo’lgan paytlarda, atrofga

00:06:57.496 --> 00:06:59.454
qaramagan bo’lardik, bizning o’zimiz

00:06:59.454 --> 00:07:01.829
yordam beruvchi ekanligimizni
anglaganimizda.